title: VonZipper : Christian Wach in the Metal Stache
description: When it's time to wipe away your inhibitions and moonwalk your way into the limelight, dress real neat from your shades to your feet in the Metal Stache. You can go where you want to, because this alloy accoutrement ain't no safety dance.
